---
const articles = [
  "How I evaluate technical tradeoffs",
  "Keeping frontend architecture boring in a good way",
  "Writing project case studies that show engineering judgment",
];
---

<section id="articles" class="border-y border-border bg-surface py-24 md:py-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="mb-12 max-w-[760px]">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-primary">Articles</p>
      <h2 class="mt-4 text-3xl font-bold leading-tight text-text-primary md:text-[36px]">Notes on craft and clarity.</h2>
      <p class="mt-5 text-text-secondary">
        Artikel bersifat opsional, tetapi struktur ini sudah siap untuk tulisan yang memperlihatkan cara berpikir teknis.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-3">
      {
        articles.map((title) => (
          <article class="rounded-card border border-border bg-surface p-6 shadow-soft">
            <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary">Draft topic</p>
            <h3 class="mt-3 text-[22px] font-semibold leading-tight text-text-primary">{title}</h3>
          </article>
        ))
      }
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
